data.description: Rare opportunity to own a beautiful TOWNHOME in Paragon Point that lives like a single-family home! This turnkey home has 3 large bedrooms, 3 bathrooms & laundry conveniently located on the second floor. Oversized primary bedroom with attached on suite and walk-in closet. Triple-pane windows in primary bedroom and main floor. Very Bright open concept living on main floor/kitchen with wood floors and stain steel appliances. Separate dining with new sliding glass door with 3 point locking system leading to patio & yard. Spacious attached 2-car garage and large unfinished basement to expand in the future. The basement has carpet installed and would just need a little more work to finish it out. Fresh paint throughout home and plenty of storage. Low maintenance living with landscaping and snow removal taken care of by the HOA and located on a peaceful cul de sac. HOA also includes gorgeous trails, pond, tennis courts and pool! Open house this Sunday Jan. 7th 12-2pm.
